0/ in line 106 src/meshfem3D/save_databases.f90 set : 
logical, parameter :: SAVE_MESH_AS_CUBIT = .true. 
and compile meshfem3D

1/ create interfaces or/and free surface on sphere by using: 
create_topo_sphere.f90
you could have to change R1,R2,R3 varaible and/or xmin, xmax, ymin,  ymax, dx, dy for your purpose.

In order to use in mesfem3D, only the 3nd column of outputs files *.xyz must be considered (write it in an ptehr file and fill interfaces.dat parameter file)  
